How to Ping:
admin@pa1> ping source I.P.A.D host I.P.A.D

How to SSH:
admin@pa1> ssh source I.P.A.D host I.P.A.D

Configuration:
Adding Devices:
Objects -> Addresses

Adding Services:
Objects -> Services

Adding Policies:
Policies -> Security

Setting up HA:
Device -> High Availability

Setup -> Edit

